<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PaLTM3.3.7">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>paṉṟiyumāmaiyummīṉamumākiya pāṟkaṭalvaṇṇā uṉmēl</l>
<l>kaṉṟiṉuruvākimēypulattēvanta kaḷḷamacuraṉtaṉṉai</l>
<l>ceṉṟupiṭittucciṟukkaikaḷālē viḷaṅkāyeṟintāypōlum</l>
<l>eṉṟumeṉpiḷḷaikkuttīmaikaḷceyvārkaḷ aṅṅaṉamāvārkaḷē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>You with the complexion of the milk ocean who became the boar, the tortoise, and the fish!</l>
<l>You with the little hands, approaching and seizing that demon who came in the field to graze in the form of a calf [in order to] deceive you!</l>
<l>[Now] it seems you have thrown a wood-apple fruit,</l> 
<l rend="indent">those who harass my child always end up like that!</l>
</lg>
